- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper discusses the challenge of computing graphlets on large graphs and proposes optimization techniques to improve efficiency. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper discusses the convergence of the proposed estimator. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also a less likely category but possible as the paper discusses the use of APIs for web crawling to obtain graph topology.
